Since Version 1.3:

	Faster loading of tweets by requesting compressed streams from Twitter.
	Spanish translation
	Chicken noises are enabled by default.
	Swipe Menu support (swipe on a cell to launch it)
	Retweeting automatically stars a tweet (configurable)
	Avatars with alpha no longer get a gray background
	UI touchups
	Several bug fixes
	Can open IDNA urls (internationalized urls)
	Properly encode utf-8 tweets for oauth use	

New since version 1.0:
	Double tap on shrink removes vowels, performs common shrink operations
